{"title":"推磨的姑娘  游击区小故事","authors":["冬池"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":8,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"推磨的姑娘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"游击区小故事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬池"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人从这里过路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又沿着公路两边扫荡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推磨的姑娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一把抓住王勤同志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把蓝布衫子脱下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿在王勤同志底身上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还把一条蓝布手巾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顶在她底头上；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"衣服和手巾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都象落着一层白霜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人在小李庄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挨门搭户地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搜查一个很红的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女共产党员。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“呱达达！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呱达达！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王勤同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐在磨房里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"低着头筛面。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人过去了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王勤同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出了一口长气："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“谢谢你！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你这个聪明的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好姑娘！”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}